                    <note type="abstract" xml:id="abstract-en-1421">In hagiography: Qashish of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/217">Ḥaḥ</placeName> was a monk mentioned in <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/74">John of Ephesus</persName>'<title>Lives of the
            Eastern Saints</title>. He went on pilgrimages and helped <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/779">the Empress Theodora</persName> to build a hostel for
          the Miaphysites.</note>
